docs: Instantiates all the other contracts, and acts as a facade to interact with them.
Returns a fight replay (detailed fight description).
* `selection_lhs` - Attacker fleet composition (array with ship quantities)
* `selection_rhs` - Defender fleet composition (array with ship quantities)
* `modules_lhs` - An array that holds modules of the attacker fleet
* `modules_rhs` - An array that holds modules of the defender fleet
* `result` - A FightResult structure containing the result
name: replay

docs: Returns a fight result (without detailed fight description).
* `selection_lhs` - Attacker fleet composition (array with ship quantities)
* `selection_rhs` - Defender fleet composition (array with ship quantities)
* `modules_lhs` - An array that holds modules of the attacker fleet
* `modules_rhs` - An array that holds modules of the defender fleet
* `result` - A FightResult structure containing the result
name: replay_result

docs: Adds ship to the ship definitions
name: add_ship

docs: Registers a fleet for Ranked Defence.
* `selection` - The fleet composition of the defence
name: register_defence

docs: Unregisters a fleet from Ranked Defence.
Transfers the Defence's balance back to the caller.
name: unregister_defence

docs: Gets the registered defence of a player.
Will panic if defence has not been registered for the player.
name: get_own_defence

docs: Gets all the registered defenders (all players).
name: get_all_defenders

docs: Calculates a ranked fight between caller and another player.
* `selection` - Attacker fleet composition (array with ship quantities)
* `modules` - An array that holds modules of the attacker fleet
name: attack

docs: * `leaderboard` - A Vec containing a tuple of (player account id, player data)
name: get_leaderboard

docs: Gets caller's standing in the ranked leaderboard.
* `ranked_entry` - A PlayerData structure with the leaderboard entry
name: get_own_standing
